Name: UploadBatchServiceLogsResult
SummaryComment: The result of uploading batch service log files from a specific compute node.

Key.Name: VirtualDirectoryName
Key.SummaryComment: The virtual directory within the Azure Blob Storage container to which the Batch Service log file(s) will be uploaded.
Key.RemarksComment: The virtual directory name is part of the blob name for each log file uploaded.

Key.Name: NumberOfFilesUploaded
Key.SummaryComment: The number of log files which will be uploaded.
